column1: 1 13  Zak 9.6 This movie is just plain bad. There must be some big payola going round this awards season. Badly written, average acting at best, all the characters are unrelatable and inlikeable. 2 hours of my life wasted.  2022-02-02T21:48:13.678Z
: Unfortunately we don't have a reliable way to tell the true ratings of a movie.,
